00:14:01,752 --> 00:14:07,237
So it's just kind of like stuff you can't really find out until you run the game as

221
00:14:07,297 --> 00:14:07,837
is intended.

222
00:14:09,422 --> 00:14:16,808
Um, uh, there's a good question in chat about engineering I do want to get to but, uh, before I do, you talked to Boa before about using camera to control the mood for this game?

