237
00:15:17,625 --> 00:15:20,348
Yeah, so, that's an interesting question.

238
00:15:20,468 --> 00:15:23,911
I think like, I think a lot of this...

239
00:15:24,592 --> 00:15:25,813
Wow, how do I answer that?

240
00:15:27,522 --> 00:15:34,486
Beau and I build the game piecemeal, and it had a lot of inspirations when we started,

241
00:15:35,807 --> 00:15:40,991
but it's kind of like one step at a time, like that's working, that's not working.

242
00:15:42,072 --> 00:15:46,254
