00:22:52,661 --> 00:22:56,565
that's what causes load on the CPU when you're trying to record footage.

339
00:22:57,386 --> 00:23:05,470
Um, uh, moving... oh man, like, chat said too, we missed that beautiful, just, moment of chaos.

