00:23:09,993 --> 00:23:13,975
into the back of it, the whole, it's like that really satisfying where you're playing breakout

342
00:23:13,995 --> 00:23:19,118
and you can get a ball to bounce up under the corner. Yeah. Yeah, that's a good, yeah man,

343
00:23:19,138 --> 00:23:23,221
that's a good breakout, like, that's a good game to reference here, I think. Yes, of course,

